description:
** Cushion insert is NOT included - cover only **

name: Flat Packable iPhone stand
description:
Super slim flat-packable wooded stand for your iPhone.
It is less than 1cm thick when it is packaged/stored.

The stand is composed of two Japanese Lime plywood pieces. They are lasercut and then polished by hand with natural beeswax. They come flat in our original packaging, which makes it perfect for a small gift.

It comes in handy in various situations such as for the desk at work, watching movies with friends, using it as an alarm clock by your bed, or editing documents/blog posts anywhere as a pocket computer with a wireless keyboard.

- Dimensions: W7cm D5.5cm H4cm
- Packaged size: W14.3cm D6cm H0.9cm
- Japanese Lime plywood pieces
- Hand-polished with organic bees wax
- Made by hand at our studio in Tokyo

description: Handmade and unique. Printed on recycled book page. A little octopi romance under the sea ~ the leggy lovers are printed on a page from a vintage 1960s book in Japanese and handstamped with the heart. *Note: The exact page you receive will be different than that shown in photo, but all come from the same volume. Print will come in an acid-free poly sleeve & secure cardboard mailer, unmatted. The creator of this print has been crafting salvaged material into collage and print form for several years. This print is excellent for framing. It will fit standard 5" x 7" unmatted frames, or standard 8" x 10" matted frames (not included). Dimensions: Approx 5" x 7".
